      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature (Fraser et al. 2011, Hariharan et al. 2011) demonstrating superior NIH prediction in centrifugal pumps versus k-epsilon variants. Model-form uncertainty estimated at ±8% NIH (95% CI) from UQ campaign ensemble. Bounded uncertainty accepted at MRL 2."
