    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 guidance. Validation demonstrates RH < 1 at all 5 operating points with bounded uncertainty. The UQ campaign, documented in VR-CPB-2025-003, confirms that hemolysis predictions are robust to geometric and operational parameter variation within manufacturing tolerances. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device. Assessment accepted by V&V review board on 2025-11-14.",
